The paper deals with the operational semantics of serverless computing, which involves distributed systems and software engineering (cs.DC and cs.SE). It also discusses the interaction between serverless functions and platform services, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper evaluates the accuracy of service call graphs, which involves machine learning (cs.LG).
